                                              AttributeDescription attributeDescription)

Returns a view of attribute having a different attribute description. All operations on the returned attribute "pass-through" to the underlying attribute.

Parameters:

attributeDescription - The new attribute description for attribute, which must be compatible with attribute's attribute description.
